show.title: Kiss and Switch The Cursed Vampire

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/8abxK5
show.description: A powerful vampire king has been struck by a mysterious curse. His only hope to be freed from this dark curse lies in a chance encounter with an innocent human maiden whom he meets unexpectedly. Will the forbidden love that grows between them break the ancient curse and grant freedom to the vampire king? Or will their dangerous bond push them both to the brink of destruction?
